text: Helmut Lebert (born 18 February 1941) is a West German rower who represented the United Team of Germany. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics in Tokyo with the men's double sculls where they came fifth. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United Team of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Munich
